[X] startup items (from ctrl+shift+esc menu, and settings app)
[X] check on win firewall allowed apps
[X] system scan for any relics of "logmein" (from exam proctoring)
[X] Check USBDeview for anything abnormal
[X] Check ncpa.cpl for anything unusual
[X] Check PATH for anything unusual
[X] Check windows users list
[X] Check AD users and permissions
[X] Check defender exclusion lists and history

